The paper deals with Natural Language Understanding and response generation, which are core topics in the field of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The use of general rebuttal arguments suggests the involvement of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) techniques. The task of listening comprehension over argumentative content involves Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Natural Language Processing (cs.NE).
